title: New England Tiger Talk
description:
New England Tiger Talk, written by David C. White. Stone Cold Fox at Maude Night, UCBTNY, May 19, 2008.

Starring Sean Clements, Scott Courlander, Nate Lang, Cody Melton, and Joe Spellman. Directed by Neil W. Casey.
